 {"id":"bd-2n73.9","title":"Web UI: tools inventory + health dashboards","description":"Update the web dashboard/setup pages to show the expanded tool inventory from ACFS manifest: categories, phases, install/verify status, robot/MCP capability badges, and version/auth state. Replace hard-coded lists with manifest-driven UI. Include UI-level tests or stories for the inventory view and empty/partial states. Success: web UI reflects real tool set and exposes actionable health signals.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:38:13.571393121Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T22:52:50.309012435Z","closed_at":"2026-01-27T22:52:50.308893100Z","close_reason":"Completed web UI tool registry integration:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. Added new types to useSetup.ts\n- Added RobotModeInfo interface for machine-readable output mode specs\n- Added McpInfo interface for MCP server capabilities  \n- Extended DetectedCapabilities with robotMode and mcp fields\n- Added ToolRegistryDefinition interface for registry tool definitions\n- Added ToolRegistryResponse interface for API response\n\n### 2. Created useToolRegistry hook\n- Fetches tool definitions from /api/setup/registry endpoint\n- Returns registry, tools array, toolMap (Map<string,ToolRegistryDefinition>)\n- Handles loading state and error handling\n- Supports refresh functionality\n\n### 3. Added capability badges to ToolCard (Setup.tsx)\n- Robot mode badge shows when cli.capabilities.robotMode?.supported is true\n- MCP server badge shows when cli.capabilities.mcp?.available is true\n- Added 'info' tone to StatusPill component with blue styling\n\n### 4. Integrated registry data into Setup page\n- ToolCard now accepts optional registryTool prop\n- Uses registry display info when available, falls back to static TOOL_DISPLAY_INFO\n- isAgent detection now uses registry category when available\n- All step content components (Detect, Install, Verify) receive and pass toolMap\n\n## Files Modified\n- apps/web/src/hooks/useSetup.ts - Added types and hooks\n- apps/web/src/pages/Setup.tsx - Added registry integration\n- apps/web/src/components/ui/StatusPill.tsx - Added 'info' tone\n- apps/web/src/index.css - Added .status-pill--info styling\n\nBuild verified successful.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.9","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:47Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.9","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:47Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.9","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:47Z","created_by":"import"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.9","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:47Z","created_by":"import"}]}
